headline: Furniture Stocks Retreat After Trump Threatens Tariffs on Imports
summary: Wayfair led the decline in after-hours trading after President Trump announced a 50-day investigation to determine a tariff rate on furniture imports.

headline: REJUVENATION ANNOUNCES GRAND OPENING OF NASHVILLE STORE
